通过在[[乌尔姆|乌尔姆]]击败奥地利军队，拿破仑确保了他在一个月后在[[維也納|维也纳]]的胜利。{{Sfn|Maude|1912|loc=[https://www.archive.org/details/ulmcampaign180500mauduoft/page/252/mode/2up Chapter IX. Conclusion]|pp=252–264}}{{Sfn|Horne|2012|loc=[https://books.google.com/books?id=Bkgwds-5dskC&pg=PT116 8. On to Vienna and Austerlitz: 21 October–28 November (Part Two: Austerlitz)]|pp=116–128}}

